      "id": "d6b57545-65f6-4c39-80d5-000000000005",
      "slug": "unit-1-lesson-5",
      "title": "Detect and Fix Ledger Errors",
      "unitNumber": 1,
      "orderIndex": 5,
      "description": "Learn to spot the three most common ledger errors — misclassification, missing entries, and negative asset balances — and use Excel's Conditional Formatting to flag them automatically.",
